{"tid":2127621,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無可否認，要對抗港共鋪天蓋地洗腦愛國教育，就要學辛顯年教授果套，將共產黨 / 中國對立","createTime":"2020-07-27T12:02:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T11:13:17.000Z","uid":230104,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"dfc243997b1e1dafdcdae3fe95f8c59a9040bfc1","tid":2127621,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T12:02:15.000Z","msg":"老懵懂既完結香港基金資助嘅洗腦電視專輯，目標客戶係香港人既大中華膠，目的就係要佢哋愛中國更加要支持共產黨（呢個係共產黨多年喺中國既宣傳技倆，將共產黨=中國，黨和國家連埋一齊提起）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國而家既都做緊呢樣，刻意將共產黨同中國分開，就係要破共產黨多年既宣傳技倆<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n共產黨想要大中華膠：愛國更要支持共產黨<br />\n而美國或辛教授提醒大中華膠：愛國更要反共<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無論你係港獨支持者又好，香港人優先又好，反中反共又好， 要擊破完結基金會既洗腦宣傳，更要用辛教授呢招去分化大中華膠/愛國藍絲<br />\n<br />\n你同佢地鬥嘴，反而無作用。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/SSdJlJACKwc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FSSdJlJACKwc&d=ducsj56GsZITs%2BYA0ylwpZLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=a0bea81a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/SSdJlJACKwc</a>"},{"pid":"510a5777d10593f939870252e243298b4a122860","tid":2127621,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T12:06:10.000Z","msg":"呢招可破洗腦教育"},{"pid":"2897bb18069ec802f4c95b8bf461a4a48f600cdd","tid":2127621,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T12:08:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"780a3d1df1c2e9ccaed9e5a21ea8303a29e5d393","tid":2127621,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T12:25:09.000Z","msg":"中國係殖民者<br />\n係咪共產黨做都係一樣"},{"pid":"a46bbf7c2aaa2395902556fa49608f3e67f7dea2","tid":2127621,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"780a3d1df1c2e9ccaed9e5a21ea8303a29e5d393","tid":2127621,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T12:25:09.000Z","msg":"中國係殖民者<br />\n係咪共產黨做都係一樣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T12:29:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d675ebec22